{"tid":1967013,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"招人合作整一隻用green object做背景嘅遊戲","createTime":"2020-04-10T15:00:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T07:30:48.000Z","uid":341578,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1f1e65f4a780df38ffa8e3a208e60b69c1a4297f","tid":1967013,"uid":341578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T15:00:42.000Z","msg":"招人合作整一隻用green object做背景嘅遊戲<br />\n<br />\n想整隻Game以green object做背景，做海外文宣嘅同時增加人地對呢場運動嘅了解，玩法係係2d街景到經歷一啲劇情然後再以唔同大事件作為關卡去完成目標。我地啱啱開始左唔係好耐，暫時只係簡單整左少少Animation, inventory system, controller同埋敵人AI。<br />\n<br />\n而家有一個畫Pixel art嘅artist同一個極新手嘅Programmer，想搵programmer同可以幫手畫Pixel art嘅人加入，新手都好，可以入黎一齊傾下！如果今次開發有幸成事同埋有需要嘅話，我地可能會上kickstarter眾籌小量經費，希望有人加入之後再傾。<br />\n<br />\nProgress so far for u guys as reference:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B6MrwE1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB6MrwE1.jpg&h=93806310&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hqHeFyp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhqHeFyp.jpg&h=f940e84b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QVkWTTq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQVkWTTq.jpg&h=b12bd178&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jHw7f7C.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjHw7f7C.gif&h=e5300822&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n基本角色  animation + physics<br />\n<br />\n關卡敵人 animation + ai script<br />\n<br />\n部分場境 <br />\n遊戲物品之類 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n方便既話留個Tg"},{"pid":"dccffad0691179359a1703ffb9449b554e916e86","tid":1967013,"uid":341578,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1f1e65f4a780df38ffa8e3a208e60b69c1a4297f","tid":1967013,"uid":341578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T15:00:42.000Z","msg":"招人合作整一隻用green object做背景嘅遊戲<br />\n<br />\n想整隻Game以green object做背景，做海外文宣嘅同時增加人地對呢場運動嘅了解，玩法係係2d街景到經歷一啲劇情然後再以唔同大事件作為關卡去完成目標。我地啱啱開始左唔係好耐，暫時只係簡